@startuml Laserpointer Presentation Flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #1f77b4
skinparam participantBackgroundColor #e1f5ff
skinparam participantBorderColor #01579b
skinparam noteBkgColor #fff9c4
skinparam noteBorderColor #f57f17

title Laser Pointer System - Presentation Flow

actor User
participant "Anwendung" as App
participant "laser.py" as Laser
participant "Qt Thread" as Qt
participant "LaserOverlay" as Overlay
participant "Bildschirm" as Screen

== PHASE 1: Initialisierung ==
autonumber
User -> App: "Laserpointer aktivieren"
App -> Laser: **StartLaserpointer()**
activate Laser
    Laser --> Laser: overlay existiert?
    Laser -> Qt: 🧵 Starte Daemon-Thread
    activate Qt
        Qt -> Qt: QApplication initialisieren
        Qt -> Overlay: 🎨 Erstelle LaserOverlay
        activate Overlay
            note over Overlay
            • Lade Einstellungen (Farbe, Größe)
            • Fenster: frameless, fullscreen, immer oben
            • Mache clickthrough (transparent für Cursor)
            • Starte Timer (fade, trail)
            end note
            Overlay -> Screen: 📺 show()
        deactivate Overlay
        Qt --> Laser: ✅ overlay_ready
    deactivate Qt
Laser --> App: ✔ Starting erfolg!
deactivate Laser

== PHASE 2: Position Update (kontinuierlich) ==
autonumber
loop 🔄 Mehrmals pro Sekunde
    User -> App: Mausposition
    App -> Laser: **UpdateLaserpointer(pos)**
    activate Laser
        Laser -> Overlay: updatePos(norm_x, norm_y)
        activate Overlay
            note over Overlay: Thread-safe via Signal/Slot
            Overlay -> Overlay: 📍 Berechne Pixel
            Overlay -> Overlay: 🌌 Update Trail
            Overlay -> Overlay: ⏱ Reset Fade-Timer
            Overlay -> Overlay: 🎨 repaint() anfordern
            note over Overlay: paintEvent() wird automatisch aufgerufen
        deactivate Overlay
    Laser --> App: ✔
    deactivate Laser
end

== PHASE 3: Rendering ==
autonumber
note over Overlay: Bei repaint() aufgerufen
activate Overlay
    note over Overlay
    ⚙ Style laden (default/trail/simple)
    end note
    opt Style: "default"
        Overlay -> Overlay: 🌟 Glow-Gradient malen
        Overlay -> Overlay: 🔴 Core-Gradient malen
    end
    opt Style: "trail"
        loop Für alle Trail-Punkte
            Overlay -> Overlay: ✨ Verblasste Punkte zeichnen
        end
    end
    Overlay -> Screen: 📺 Rendern
deactivate Overlay

== PHASE 4: Fade-Out (nach Inaktivität) ==
autonumber
note over Overlay: Nach ~1 Sekunde Inaktivität
Overlay -> Overlay: ⏱ Inaktivitäts-Timer läuft ab
Overlay -> Overlay: 👻 fadeout_start()
loop opacity > 0 (alle 50ms)
    Overlay -> Overlay: ⬇ opacity -= 0.05
    Overlay -> Overlay: 🎨 repaint()
end
note over Overlay: Laserpointer langsam ausgeblendet

== PHASE 5: Beenden ==
autonumber
User -> App: "Laserpointer deaktivieren"
App -> Laser: **ClearLaserpointer()**
activate Laser
    Laser -> Overlay: close()
    Laser -> Laser: 🗑 cleanup
Laser --> App: ✔ Cleared
deactivate Laser

@enduml
